(7)
\begin{align*}
L: &[s^2C(s)-sc(0)-\dot{c}(0)]+5[sC(s)-c(0)]+[4C(s)]\\
&(s^2 + 5s + 4)C(s)-(s + 5)c(0)-\dot{c}(0)=2(s + 2)R(s)\\
C(s)&=\frac{2(s + 2)}{s^2 + 5s + 4}\cdot\frac{1}{s}-\frac{s + 5}{s^2 + 5s + 4}=\frac{-s^2-3s + 4}{s(s + 1)(s + 4)}
\end{align*}
其中初条件引起的自由响应部分
\begin{align*}
C_0(s)&=\frac{-(s + 5)}{(s + 1)(s + 4)}=\frac{C_1}{s + 1}+\frac{C_2}{s + 4}=\frac{-4}{3}\cdot\frac{1}{s + 1}+\frac{1}{3}\cdot\frac{1}{s + 4}\\
C_1&=\lim_{s\rightarrow -1}\frac{-(s + 5)}{s + 4}=-\frac{4}{3}\\
C_2&=\lim_{s\rightarrow -4}\frac{-(s + 5)}{s + 1}=\frac{1}{3}\\
c_0(t)&=\frac{-4}{3}e^{-t}+\frac{1}{3}e^{-4t}\\
c(t)&=c_r(t)+c_0(t)=\left(1-\frac{2}{3}e^{-t}-\frac{1}{3}e^{-4t}\right)-\left(\frac{4}{3}e^{-t}-\frac{1}{3}e^{-4t}\right)=1 - 2e^{-t}
\end{align*}

依题意，$G(s)=\frac{10}{0.2s + 1}$，$\begin{cases}T = 0.2\\K = 10\end{cases}$，闭环系统应满足$\begin{cases}T^{*}=0.1T = 0.02\\K^{*}=K = 10\end{cases}$。
\begin{align*}
\Phi(s)&=\frac{K_{O}G(s)}{1 + K_{H}G(s)}\\
&=\frac{\frac{10K_{O}}{0.2s + 1}}{1 + \frac{10K_{H}}{0.2s + 1}}\\
&=\frac{10K_{O}}{0.2s + 1 + 10K_{H}}\\
&=\frac{\frac{10K_{O}}{1 + 10K_{H}}}{\frac{0.2}{1 + 10K_{H}}s + 1}
\end{align*}
由$\begin{cases}\frac{0.2}{1 + 10K_{H}} = T^{*}=0.02\\\frac{10K_{O}}{1 + 10K_{H}} = K^{*}=10\end{cases}$，解得$\begin{cases}K_{H}=0.9\\K_{O}=10\end{cases}$。
